&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span&gt;Project Proposal: Extra-Universal Hume Control Applications in the mitigation of Mass anomalous activity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span&gt;Outline&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The use of a HSURRD Device has been shown effective in mitigating the ongoing Extra-universal Mass Interaction Event (EUMIE) &lt;sup&gt;[1][2]&lt;/sup&gt;. The activation of such a device would constitute the aversion of a ZK-Class &amp;quot;Reality Failure&amp;quot; Scenario, though would cause a ZK-Class event elsewhere. The structural components of the construction would be as follows &amp;#8230;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;#8230;Associated Papers:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[1] &lt;em&gt;An Explanatory Model for current Increases in Anomalous Activity&lt;/em&gt; - Aleel et al., 2021, Site 102 Acedemic Output, cited 11 times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[2] &lt;em&gt;Outline of &#039;Hume Siphoning Universal Realistic Reset Device&amp;quot; (HSURRD)&lt;/em&gt; - Gears et al., 2021, Site 19 Academic Output, cited 2 times.&lt;/p&gt;
